{
  "texts": [
    "The sexual harassment behaviour such as rape, verbal and non-verbal activity, can be noticed in the word cloud.",
    "For the second model, the dataset consists of 65 instances with the label 'Physical' and 43 instances with the label 'Non-physical.",
    "The feature engineering technique, the Term Frequency/ Inverse Document Frequency (TFIDF) is applied.",
    "After that, the Principal Component Analysis (PCA) is applied for dimensionality reduction.",
    "The 108 instances are then split into train dataset and test dataset, where 30% of the dataset is used for testing the performance of the model."
  ]
}